<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p><strong>TABLE III</strong> Projected Water Needs for Orange County Given the Following Scenario:</p>

<p>* No increase in consumption per capita from 120 gpcpd.</p>

<p>* By 1980, all toilets will be reduced by &frac34; gallons, 50% of all showers will have water-saving heads. Starting in 1980, all new construction will have watersaving shower heads and low flush (2&frac12; gallon) toilets.</p>

